---
// Clickable thumbnail preview that opens the session report modal.
// Renders a scaled-down version of the actual report first page
// so visitors immediately recognize it as a professional document.
---

<button
  id="open-report-preview"
  type="button"
  class="report-preview-trigger group"
  aria-haspopup="dialog"
  aria-controls="session-report-modal"
>
  <!-- Scaled-down page rendering -->
  <div class="report-preview-frame" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="report-preview-page">
      <div class="preview-content">
        <!-- Header -->
        <p class="preview-title">Session Notes</p>
        <div class="preview-meta">
          <p><strong>Date:</strong> January 5, 2026</p>
          <p><strong>Duration:</strong> ~59 min</p>
          <p><strong>Attendees:</strong> Andrea Goulet, Alex</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="preview-hr" />

        <!-- Overview -->
        <p class="preview-heading">Overview</p>
        <p class="preview-body">Alex spent ~15–16 hours on his blog during the holiday break and feels proud of the progress. The session explored why budgeting 20 hours (vs. 1 hour) shifted his emotional experience from embarrassment to pride, identified a sunk cost fallacy pattern around rabbit holes, and established experiments for estimation and context capture.</p>

        <hr class="preview-hr" />

        <!-- Experimental Design -->
        <p class="preview-heading">Experimental Design</p>

        <p class="preview-subheading">1. Friction Point</p>
        <p class="preview-body">Estimating accurately and avoiding rabbit holes that delay launching the blog.</p>

        <p class="preview-subheading">2. Context</p>
        <table class="preview-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Theme</th><th>Description</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Previous session</td><td>Felt embarrassed about lack of progress when estimating 1 hour for tasks</td></tr>
            <tr><td>This session</td><td>Felt proud after budgeting 20 hours and spending ~15–16</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Work blocks</td><td>Morning sessions continue to be effective; context switching is expensive</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Documentation</td><td>Writing tickets/documentation "doesn't feel like work," contributing to sunk cost trap</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Work situation</td><td>Increased estimation requests at work</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p class="preview-subheading">3. Variables</p>
        <table class="preview-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Variable</th><th>Observed Outcome</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Time budget (1 hr vs 20 hrs)</td><td>20 hrs → pride; 1 hr → embarrassment</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Doom scrolling replacement</td><td>Successfully swapped for blog work multiple times</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Breaking work into pieces</td><td>Easier to estimate smaller chunks</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hover overlay -->
    <div class="preview-overlay">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8" />
        <line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65" />
        <line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14" />
        <line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Label -->
  <span class="report-preview-label">View Sample Report</span>
</button>

<style>
  .report-preview-trigger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* The visible frame that clips the scaled content */
  .report-preview-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 12rem;
    height: 15.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.12),
      0 4px 8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .report-preview-trigger:hover .report-preview-frame,
  .report-preview-trigger:focus-visible .report-preview-frame {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.15),
      0 8px 24px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.08);
  }

  .report-preview-trigger:focus-visible {
    outline: none;
  }

  .report-preview-trigger:focus-visible .report-preview-frame {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-teal-600);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  /* The "page" that gets scaled down */
  .report-preview-page {
    width: 40rem;
    background: white;
    transform: scale(0.3);
    transform-origin: top left;
  }

  .preview-content {
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--color-teal-950);
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  /* Typography at full-size (will be scaled to 0.3) */
  .preview-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .preview-meta {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .preview-meta p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-teal-800);
    margin: 0.1rem 0;
  }

  .preview-hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-teal-200);
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .preview-heading {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .preview-subheading {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-teal-800);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .preview-body {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .preview-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .preview-table {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .preview-table th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-teal-200);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--color-teal-400);
  }

  .preview-table td {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-teal-200);
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  /* Fade at bottom to suggest continuation */
  .report-preview-frame::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, white);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Hover overlay */
  .preview-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(0, 54, 64, 0.5);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    color: white;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .report-preview-trigger:hover .preview-overlay,
  .report-preview-trigger:focus-visible .preview-overlay {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .report-preview-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-teal-800);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: dotted;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .report-preview-trigger:hover .report-preview-label {
    color: var(--color-teal-950);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .report-preview-frame {
      transition: none;
    }
    .preview-overlay {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
